# IntakeAI — Intelligent Patient Intake Agent for Home Health Agencies
# Hackathon: AI Healthcare Hack NYC (Arya Health × Twilio)
# Build time: 5 hours, 4 engineers, Cursor

## PROJECT CONTEXT

This is a healthcare AI hackathon project. We are building an intelligent patient intake agent for home health agencies. The system handles the entire intake workflow — from receiving a patient referral (via phone call or fax) to making an admit/decline decision — using voice AI, document intelligence, and real-time eligibility checking.

The core value proposition: home health agencies lose 36% of patient referrals because they're too slow to respond. Our system picks up the phone 24/7, processes faxes automatically, checks eligibility in real-time, and gives answers in minutes instead of hours.

This is NOT a deployed production system. It runs locally with Docker Compose + ngrok for Twilio connectivity. But it must be demo-quality — judges will call the Twilio number live.

